   9  * When you capture a photo in KiwiCam or import one from your library, the image stays on your device.
  10: * If you choose to apply an AI style, the app compresses the image and transmits it—together with the style prompt—to our AI processor (AIProxy/Replicate) so the transformation can run on Replicate's infrastructure using Google's Nano Banana model.
